### GET PRIORITIES ###
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/priorities
Authorization: Bearer {{Access_token}}

### CREATE TICKET ### 
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/tickets
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{Access_token}}

