### LIST TICKETS ###
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/tickets
Authorization: Bearer {{Access_token}}

### GET STATUSES ###
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/status
Authorization: Bearer {{Access_token}}


### GET USERS ###
